data.description: Here's your chance to have it all in North Columbus! Come see this amazing Maple Ridge home overlooking the 10th green! Step inside to the two story foyer, wood floors, great room featuring cathedral ceiling,  fireplace and custom built in cabinetry. The spacious kitchen features granite counters, stainless appliances, island, pantry, butler's pantry in the attached laundry room, all overlooking the breakfast room and back patio. The main level master suite offers an incredible, recently remodeled bath with separate shower, tub and double vanities as well as two large walk in closets. Upstairs you'll find a second master suite with a oversized walk in closet along with two more large bedrooms and a hall bath. This home also includes new energy efficient windows throughout and a nearly brand new roof! Enjoy morning coffee on the back patio overlooking the level and fenced yard! The neighborhood pool, golf and tennis are just steps away! Don't miss your best life in this amazing home!
